        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Examining Opioid Treatment Infrastructure Act of </b><b>2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Government Accountability Office to report on the availability of and unmet need for substance use disorder treatment and recovery services, including for specified populations. The report must also address barriers to real-time reporting of drug overdoses at the federal, state, and local levels.</p>]]>
        </text>
